# Sample Cake configuration file
# ------------------------------
# 
# For detailed documentation see CakeLoadConfig.cmake
# The list if variables:
#
# ``CAKE_BINARY_DIR_PREFIX``
# ``CAKE_CMAKE_OPTIONS``
